Johnny Clegg who was diagnosed with stage two pancreatic cancer last year has tragically died. In 2015 he did this interview with CNBC Africa in which he shared his incredible story after more than 40 years in the music industry JOHNNY CLEGG 1953 – 2019  Johnny Clegg who was diagnosed with stage two pancreatic cancer last year has tragically died. In 2015 he did this interview with CNBC Africa in which he shared his incredible story after more than 40 years in the music industry. 